{"tid":2074704,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"13 吋 MacBook Pro 和 24 吋 iMac 似乎會先發 ARM 處理器","createTime":"2020-06-22T10:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T06:07:36.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd24bac25454ed971784b0e2705ddb1300c632dc","tid":2074704,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/a1eb0210-b42e-11ea-baff-6d05ed0c8548\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2Fa1eb0210-b42e-11ea-baff-6d05ed0c8548&h=59bf9b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今夜 1 時，就是 Apple 線上版 WWDC20 正式展開的時間，在活動之前，名分析師郭明錤也要來爆料。他表示基於供應鍊的消息，Apple 最快會在今秋推出兩款搭載自家 ARM 架構 Mac 產品，首發的會是 13 吋 MacBook Pro 和 24 吋 iMac。<br />\n<br />\nApple 會捨棄 Intel，改用自家 ARM 架構處理器的說法，近日甚囂塵上。郭明錤更表示，新 Mac 電腦會因為 ARM 處理器而有 50% 至 100% 的效能提升。同時也預測會在 2021 年年中，推出全新款的 MacBook，或許就是有可能把 12 吋 MacBook 帶回來吧。據 Bloomberg 的說法，Apple 的首款 ARM 桌機處理器將會有 12 核心之多呢。<br />\n<br />\n是說，先假定 Apple 自家的 ARM 架構處理器當真會在年內亮相，那他們會先以小尺寸 MBP 和家用 AIO 的iMac來當示範作也是合理不過的，因為 ARM 架構的優點就是在相對低耗的裝置裡能帶來規格優勢，同時也有續航力方面的好處。WWDC20 就在轉角，讓我們來期待會否有相關的消息公佈吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/kuo-arm-imac-macbook-pro-claims-033016091.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fkuo-arm-imac-macbook-pro-claims-033016091.html&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=2cc94174\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/kuo-arm-imac-macbook-pro-claims-033016091.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac7f702a360a0eb158c76f515c8dafe648f3be01","tid":2074704,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"ARM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該係用返iPad 啲Software?"},{"pid":"e6742c2aed51d5d564dde6e92b0aef63c5011763","tid":2074704,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"到我黎講只要support microsoft office咁應該冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ca335fa004df861b3bd3111584f24ef018a28e","tid":2074704,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c654fa3fd4d272171a5ee0cacf305175384e0","tid":2074704,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7f702a360a0eb158c76f515c8dafe648f3be01","tid":2074704,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"ARM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該係用返iPad 啲Software?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"應該有個middleware？"},{"pid":"1f636c2266d5d0679f900333b67f9486e66d2c8a","tid":2074704,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"iPad越整越似MacBook<br />\nMacBook越整越似iPad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea377173b3d38466e8298641d742f22dfe831c4","tid":2074704,"uid":329544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f636c2266d5d0679f900333b67f9486e66d2c8a","tid":2074704,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"iPad越整越似MacBook<br />\nMacBook越整越似iPad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"咁好正常，iOS本身就係奄咗的OS X，而家兩樣嘢用番一樣的CPU，即係得得周邊硬體唔一樣<br />\nApple行咗呢步，應該要睇番其他廠點打，因為Apple又可以cut舊電的大小，風扇可能都唔要，la